OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778573162
OL,3,CThousands of job losses predicted in
OL,4,CWales as fallout from Iran War
OL,6,FNearly 6,000 people in south Wales are
OL,7,Fat risk of losing their jobs due to
OL,8,Fthe economic fallout of the Iran War,
OL,9,Faccording to a report.
OL,11,FThe new report by economic forecasting
OL,12,Fgroup the Item Club found that Britain
OL,13,Fis predicted to lose 163,000 jobs in
OL,14,F2026, with south Wales being
OL,15,Fhighlighted as among the worst places
OL,16,Faffected.
OL,18,FThe area is expected to face 5,700 job
OL,19,Flosses due to its "low income" status.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
