OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778573162
OL,3,CThousands of job losses predicted in
OL,4,CWales as fallout from Iran War
OL,6,FAs a major industrial region, south
OL,7,FWales has also suffered from the high
OL,8,Fand volatile energy price changes.
OL,9,FThis means that employees working in
OL,10,Fthe manufacturing and construction
OL,11,Fsectors will be the most impacted.
OL,13,FThe report also predicted that while
OL,14,Fpublicly-funded industries like
OL,15,Feducation, public administration and
OL,16,Fhealth and social work are expected to
OL,17,Fhire more jobs throughout 2026, this
OL,18,Fwill not be enough to offset wider
OL,19,Flosses.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778573162
OL,3,CThousands of job losses predicted in
OL,4,CWales as fallout from Iran War
OL,6,FIt also warns that the gape in living
OL,7,Fstandards across the UK will widen due
OL,8,Fto the Iran conflict.
OL,10,FLow income areas will see families
OL,11,Fsuffer the steepest hikes in the cost-
OL,12,Fof-living as more of their spending
OL,13,Fgoes on food, fuel and energy bills,
OL,14,Fwhich are also set to see price rises.
OL,16,FTim Lyne, Economic Adviser to the Item
OL,17,FClub, explained why it is the lowest
OL,18,Fincome areas who will take the biggest
OL,19,Fhit.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778573162
OL,3,CThousands of job losses predicted in
OL,4,CWales as fallout from Iran War
OL,6,FHe said: "Some of the lowest income
OL,7,Fregions will feel the biggest effects
OL,8,Fof the manufacturing and construction
OL,9,Fsectors reducing headcount in the face
OL,10,Fof rising energy prices and supply
OL,11,Fchain disruption.
OL,13,F"While consumers in these areas
OL,14,Ftypically have less rainy-day savings,
OL,15,Fwhich will reduce spending in the
OL,16,Fretail and hospitality sectors."
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@AOUxD@`O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
