CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778573162
OL,3,CThousands of job losses predicted in
OL,4,CWales as fallout from Iran War
OL,6,FA UK Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Recent figures show that there was an
OL,8,Fimprovement in the labour market at
OL,9,Fthe beginning of the year with
OL,10,Funemployment falling below 5%, and
OL,11,F332,000 more people in work than a
OL,12,Fyear ago.
OL,14,F"But we cannot escape the effects of
OL,15,Fthe war in the Middle East which are
OL,16,Flikely to feed through to prices and
OL,17,Femployment in the coming months.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
