OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778573162
OL,3,CThousands of job losses predicted in
OL,4,CWales as fallout from Iran War
OL,6,F"We will do everything we can to
OL,7,Fsupport the country through this
OL,8,Fperiod, including by slashing energy
OL,9,Fbills by up to 25% for 10,000
OL,10,Fmanufacturers.
OL,12,F"Our mission for clean power by 2030
OL,13,Fwill get us off the rollercoaster of
OL,14,Ffossil fuel prices, to cut bills for
OL,15,Fbusinesses and households for good."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@dO]
